(Translated by Google) Naturally, there are many shops that serve hamburgers in Hawaii, and there are many hamburger shops. The Honolulu Burger Company is one of the hamburger specialty stores. Founded in 2010.  Is it a little out of the center of Waikiki, and is it easy to understand the north side of Ala Moana Shopping Center? It's a bit far to walk, so it seems better to use The Bus or Biki (bicycle). Because of such a place, it is also characterized by relatively many locomotives.  The hamburger menu is broadly divided into simple HAMBURGER and HBC (Honolulu Burger Company) specialty burgers. Simple burgers are $ 8.89 for single patties, $ 11.89 for double patties and $ 14.89 for triple patties. Since one patty is 1/3 pound, it is about 150 grams. A triple is one pound, so it exceeds 450 grams.  Honolulu Burger Company is also a specialty burger, and the signboard menu is “BLUE HAWAII BURGER”. Hamburger with a unique flavor using blue cheese and bacon. $ 10.89. After that, there were a lot of menus such as “HAWAIIAN BRIAN BURGER”, “ALOHA ELVIS BURGER”, “MISO KUTIE BURGER”, but there are explanations, so let's select them carefully. (If you notice, there may be a line behind you!)  So I ordered "MUSHROOM MUSHROOM BURGER: $ 11.89" and "LOCO MOCO BURGER: $ 12.89". Add $ 3 for fries and drinks.  Mushroom Mushroom Burger Burger is a dish made from sauteed mushrooms and sautéed onions together with Swiss cheese on a patty. The taste of this mushroom spreads without being stiff. A simple but delicious burger. Come if you like mushrooms.  Loco Moco Burger is a regular hamburger with bacon, spam and fried eggs. Plenty of gravy sauce from above, it looks gorgeous, but it feels junky. A perfect dish for gravy sauce lovers. However, it is difficult to eat a little.  One of my favorite hamburger shops. If you are interested, please.  (Original) ハワイには当然のことながらハンバーガーを出すお店が多く、またハンバーガー屋さんも少なくない。ここホノルルバーガーカンパニーもハンバーガー専門店の一つ。2010年創業。  少しだけワイキキの中心地からは外れており、アラモアナショッピングセンターの北の方といえばわかりやすいか。歩いていくにはちょっと遠いので、The Busを使うか、Biki（自転車）で行くのが良さそう。そんな場所のためか、比較的ロコが多いのも特徴。  ハンバーガーメニューは、シンプルなHAMBURGERとHBC（ホノルルバーガーカンパニー）のスペシャリティバーガーに大きく分かれる。シンプルなハンバーガーはシングルパティが8.89ドル、ダブルパティが11.89ドル、トリプルパティが14.89ドルだ。パティ1枚は1/3パウンドなので、約150グラム。トリプルなんていうと1パウンドなので450グラム超え。  ホノルルバーガーカンパニーはスペシャリティバーガーも面白くて、看板メニューは「BLUE HAWAII BURGER（ブルーハワイバーガー）」だ。ブルーチーズとベーコンを使った独特の風味が特徴のハンバーガー。10.89ドル。あとは「HAWAIIAN BRIAN BURGER」や「ALOHA ELVIS BURGER」「MISO KUTIE BURGER」など気になるメニューはたくさんあったが、説明文がついているので、じっくり読みつつ選ぼう。（気づいたら後ろに行列ができてるかもだけど！）  ということでオーダーしたのは「MUSHROOM MUSHROOM BURGER（マッシュルームマッシュルームバーガー）：11.89ドル」と「LOCO MOCO BURGER（ロコモコバーガー）：12.89ドル」。プラス3ドルでフライとドリンクをセットにできる。  マッシュルームマッシュルームバーガーバーガーはソテーにしたマッシュルームを同じくソテーした玉ねぎと合わせて、スイスチーズでまとめてパティに乗っけた一品。マッシュルームの量をケチっていないのできのこの旨味が広がる。シンプルだけどコクが合って美味しいハンバーガー。マッシュルーム好きなら是非。  ロコモコバーガーは通常のハンバーガーにベーコンとスパム、そして目玉焼きを。上からグレービーソースをたっぷりかけて、見た目も派手だけど、食べごたえもジャンキーな感じだ。グレービーソース好きにはぴったりな一品。ただ、ちょっと食べづらいのが難点。  個人的には結構好きなハンバーガー屋さんの一つ。気になる方はぜひ。

Such sweet customer service! Extensive menu and loved the food. Especially love that this is a local company hiring local folks and using local products. Wish they were in a bigger space, with more seating & more parking. Something that had climate control would it be helpful, and I'm sure that the kitchen would appreciate some climate control too. Those folks are working hard back there in some hot conditions!  Charming. Unique flavor combinations. Huge, huge menu. But it all riffs off of the same local grass-fed beef patty, so I can see how it's possible to have variety but not over-tax the inventory/keep the walk-in refrigerator & food fresh. I think a decent value for the product. I get that it is pricey, but it ain't MickeyD's.  Free parking in small lot in back. A few on-street spots in front of shop. Best bet is to hop on a Biki and park it at the bike stand in front of the shop. A few small outdoor tables available too, if you'd rather lean it next to you.  Delivery available with The Bite Squad, etc.  Recommend ordering ahead. Expect a small wait.  5Star app participant with comparatively generous rewards.  4 stars for good food & customer service. Down a star for cleanliness issues. Company is expanding, so will wait to see if quality holds. Happy that a local company is getting bigger! More power to them! (Uh, now can you pls clean your a/c?) ;)
